{"tid":1692680,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[重開] 女示威者證實被強姦。男示威者墮樓變植物人。夫婦被藍絲企圖謀殺。你答我停止升級嘅理由？","createTime":"2019-11-04T07:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T16:37:18.000Z","uid":167548,"like":161,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"edd5acadb6abe68db57d1a3bc1e1bfb21375d4e1","tid":1692680,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"你發唔發覺所有散播仇恨嘅新聞各大媒體都有意沒意盡量淡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n急症室醫生FB: 強姦事件唔係傳言<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1688441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1688441</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【正名】將軍澳手足唔係意外墮樓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【七區反警暴●太古】夫婦遇襲！丈夫中兩刀穿肺命危 妻情況嚴重<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你明唔明升級並不單單損害支那利益, 更損害美國利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">但是升級卻是香港斬掉重煉浴火重生必然嘅一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n第一位爆眼男教師引起嘅回響細到睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一位爆眼女FA, 即時引起812佔領機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一位被強姦嘅女手足一啲浪花都見唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一間傳媒都沒報道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話比我聽點解有醫生冒險指證都沒報出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚製造恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚嚇親和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身邊有淺黃朋友竟然唔知道呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果今晚仍然見唔到蘋果報出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地真是諗下究竟中美兩方擺香港上台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連香港版光洲事件都可以重現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母南韓反美情緒就是因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒錯, 我唔否認美國是香港嘅盟友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是你要記住得香港人是全心全意為香港好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後通牒: 1104 HKT1700 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人 攬炒！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">每日初步等埋中學生放學就遍地開花。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6d4739aa870e65b8882f680fe0f84a269de735ad","tid":1692680,"uid":167548,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:49:39.000Z","msg":"女示威者證據被強姦。男示威者墮樓變植物人。夫婦被藍絲企圖謀殺。你答我停止升級嘅理由？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692580</a>"},{"pid":"8238a403a38f1f232883b8f679dcb13879dd9cc9","tid":1692680,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db58a8e0bc7caf0585a9518c411da12d60e00f4","tid":1692680,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"求幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9c7ad7c8c88d498a205c82f93308b171b31966","tid":1692680,"uid":23023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de72291dac7f216d22f869b884bc872cb763e440","tid":1692680,"uid":167548,"like":0